POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "1234567890",
  "mobile": "0877777777",
  "cardId": "7777777777777",
  "password": "numbersonly"
}

### 22. Profile with very long username
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "very_long_username_that_might_cause_issues_but_should_still_work_fine",
  "mobile": "0888888888",
  "cardId": "8888888888888",
  "password": "verylongusername"
}

